Usage: addBumpConnectTargetConstraint [-help] {-bump <string> | -selected } {{-instName <string> [{-pinName <string> | -netName <string>} [-portNum <integer>]]} | -PGConnectType {ioring corering stripe iopin}}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-PGConnectType {ioring corering stripe iopin}
                        # pg connect type (enum, required)
-bump <string>          # add bump connect target constraint on specified bump
                        # (string list, required)
-instName <string>      # connect target inst (string, required)
-netName <string>       # connect target net name (string, optional)
-pinName <string>       # connect target pin name (string, optional)
-portNum <integer>      # connect target port number (int, optional)
-selected               # add bump connect target constraint on selected bumps
                        # (bool, required)